EndEventUnits:
	UNIT Teacher Veteran 0x40 Level(10,Ally,False)     [13,2] 0b 0x0 0x0 0x0 [IronLance, SteelBlade] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
	UNIT HeroChar UpstartM 0x40 Level(3,Ally,False)     [12,3] 0b 0x0 0x0 0x0 [IronBow, IronSword, HerosFlair, Restore] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
	UNIT Dragon Headsman 0x40 Level(3,Ally,False)     [12,1] 0b 0x0 0x0 0x0 [SteelAxe, SlimAxe, Bomb, Vulnerary] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
